{"id":311840,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-上海民众再次呼吁停止政治迫害，释放良/","date":"2013-09-03T11:04:13Z","modified":"2013-09-03T11:04:13Z","title":"维权网 | 上海民众再次呼吁停止政治迫害，释放良心犯（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员雷鸣报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>日下午，上海<span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span>多位民</span><span>众</span><span>代表聚集上海市人民公</span><span>园</span><span>广</span><span>场，</span><span>拉</span><span>横</span><span>幅</span><span>声</span><span>援正在</span><span>遭受牢</span><span>狱</span><span>之苦的</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>捍</span><span>卫</span><span>者</span><span>：“李化平、</span><span>杨</span><span>林、</span><span>张</span><span>林、</span><span>黄</span><span>文</span><span>勋</span><span>、郭泉、魏勤、王扣</span><span>玛</span><span>、</span><span>丁家喜、</span><span>张</span><span>向忠、</span><span>赵</span><span>常</span><span>青</span><span>、</span><span>刘晓</span><span>波、</span><span>陈卫</span><span>、</span><span>陈</span><span>克</span><span>贵</span><span>、</span><span>郭</span><span>飞</span><span>雄、</span><span>刘</span><span>萍、</span><span>许</span><span>志永</span><span>”等。上海民</span><span>众</span><span>代表</span><span>们</span><span>强烈要求停止迫害立即</span><span>释</span><span>放</span><span>所有被</span><span>关</span><span>押的民主</span><span>人士、</span><span>维权</span><span>人士、</span><span>异议</span><span>人士</span><span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家认为，民</span><span>众</span><span>的生存</span><span>权</span><span>都得不到保障</span><span>的主要因素是什</span><span>么</span><span>？</span><span>是</span><span>独</span><span>裁</span><span>专</span><span>制</span><span>造成</span><span>权</span><span>大于法、</span><span>腐</span><span>败</span><span>泛</span><span>滥</span><span>、民不聊生。</span><span>越</span><span>来</span><span>越多的民</span><span>众</span><span>正在</span><span>觉</span><span>醒，渴望民主的信念越</span><span>来</span><span>越强烈。民</span><span>众</span><span>相信只有</span><span>自己投票</span><span>选举</span><span>出</span><span>来</span><span>的人</span><span>执</span><span>政</span><span>才不</span><span>会</span><span>强</span><span>抢</span><span>掠</span><span>夺</span><span>民</span><span>众</span><span>合法的私有</span><span>财产</span><span>和</span><span>恶</span><span>意</span><span>剥夺公民</span><span>依法享有的一切</span><span>权</span><span>利。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>众</span><span>所周知，</span><span>中</span><span>国</span><span>是</span><span>联</span><span>合</span><span>国</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>理事</span><span>会</span><span>的成</span><span>员国</span><span>，今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span>份联</span><span>合</span><span>国对</span><span>中</span><span>国</span><span>普遍定期</span><span>审议</span><span>。但中国政府却仍然不停地</span><span>抓</span><span>捕</span><span>关</span><span>押</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>捍</span><span>卫</span><span>者和</span><span>异议</span><span>人士</span><span>，不遵守《世界人</span><span>权</span><span>宣言》、</span><span>国际</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>公</span><span>约</span><span>和</span><span>联</span><span>合</span><span>国</span><span>《人</span><span>权</span><span>捍</span><span>卫</span><span>者宣言》。在短短</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>个</span><span>月</span><span>内</span><span>已在全</span><span>国抓</span><span>捕了</span><span>数</span><span>百名人</span><span>权</span><span>捍</span><span>卫</span><span>者（其中已正式逮捕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多人、刑事拘留至少有<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>多人、行政拘留多</span><span>达数</span><span>百人）。和</span><span>谐</span><span>社</span><span>会</span><span>如此大</span><span>规</span><span>模</span><span>疯</span><span>狂打</span><span>压</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>捍</span><span>卫</span><span>者，大肆</span><span>抓</span><span>捕</span><span>维权</span><span>人士，制造全</span><span>国</span><span>性恐怖，</span><span>会</span><span>直接影</span><span>响</span><span>今年的普通定期</span><span>审议</span><span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>被</span><span>抓</span><span>的</span><span>这</span><span>些</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>捍</span><span>卫</span><span>者都是</span><span>满</span><span>腔</span><span>爱国热</span><span>情</span><span>，有社</span><span>会责</span><span>任感</span><span>。他（</span><span>她</span><span>）</span><span>们</span><span>不但无罪，而且有功。在民主</span><span>国</span><span>家受到</span><span>称赞</span><span>，而在</span><span>独</span><span>裁</span><span>国</span><span>家却被坐牢。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海民</span><span>众</span><span>强烈要求政府停止</span><span>打</span><span>压</span><span>迫害人</span><span>权</span><span>捍</span><span>卫</span><span>者和公民</span><span>维权</span><span>行</span><span>动</span><span>，</span><span>切</span><span>实</span><span>履行我</span><span>国</span><span>《</span><span>宪</span><span>法》保</span><span>护</span><span>公民</span><span>权</span><span>利和人身自由的承</span><span>诺</span><span>，</span><span>释</span><span>放一切被</span><span>关</span><span>押的</span><span>人</span><span>权</span><span>捍</span><span>卫</span><span>者</span><span>；依法追究那些</span><span>违宪违</span><span>法，</span><span>践</span><span>踏</span><span>法律、侵犯人</span><span>权</span><span>、激化社</span><span>会</span><span>冲突的部</span><span>门</span><span>和</span><span>个</span><span>人的</span><span>责</span><span>任。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-w3hOXx7vdB4/UiWWbvfycMI/AAAAAAAAnsA/2rDB2_DUe6Y/s1600/P1030519.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"206\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-w3hOXx7vdB4/UiWWbvfycMI/AAAAAAAAnsA/2rDB2_DUe6Y/s320/P1030519.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-5VYvruOWUKc/UiWWXp5yT9I/AAAAAAAAnr4/LE_uiYvosTI/s1600/P1030520.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"214\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-5VYvruOWUKc/UiWWXp5yT9I/AAAAAAAAnr4/LE_uiYvosTI/s320/P1030520.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></d